  "detailed_description": "A Tofu Tail is the puzzle game of a man-turned-tofu by a deceptive fox spirit, the Kitsune.<br>​Explore the surreal realms of the foxes to help Mr. Tofu break his curse!<br><br>Use your tofu brain to absorb new flavors and solve over one hundred colorful puzzles!<br>Can you outsmart the trickster foxes and escape from the ​phantasmagorical Kitsune world?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >★ Solve addicting puzzles across 100+ levels ★<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/79bd3b6c30c515146cbe93d9036908ac.poster.avif?t=1743614594\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/79bd3b6c30c515146cbe93d9036908ac.webm?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/79bd3b6c30c515146cbe93d9036908ac.mp4?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>★ Explore and experience each of the dream-like Kitsune realms ★<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/98a94ac570dbd15ee33093ae6ee967c2.poster.avif?t=1743614594\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/98a94ac570dbd15ee33093ae6ee967c2.webm?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/98a94ac570dbd15ee33093ae6ee967c2.mp4?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>★ ​Take part in a whimsical story influenced by Japanese folklore ★<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/c951180045277a9a2fa1a01dc58a6a64.poster.avif?t=1743614594\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/c951180045277a9a2fa1a01dc58a6a64.webm?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/c951180045277a9a2fa1a01dc58a6a64.mp4?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>★ Become immersed in a unique hand-drawn art style ★<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/0a5d1db28c36cf5637ee0a4c9ea6260d.poster.avif?t=1743614594\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/0a5d1db28c36cf5637ee0a4c9ea6260d.webm?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/0a5d1db28c36cf5637ee0a4c9ea6260d.mp4?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>★ Lose yourself in an imaginative and blood-pumping chiptune soundtrack ★<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/556fd8d73056b1d48d8e9609581e5f76.poster.avif?t=1743614594\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/556fd8d73056b1d48d8e9609581e5f76.webm?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/454240/extras/556fd8d73056b1d48d8e9609581e5f76.mp4?t=1743614594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2>",
